# Local agent scratch space — Claude Code worktrees, scheduled-task locks,
# etc. These are per-clone local state and must never be tracked. A past
# agent ran `git add` in the main checkout and committed 34 worktree
# directories as gitlinks; this rule + the untracking in the same commit
# (Wave 9 §17.5 audit) closes that.
.claude/
